24:36.160 --> 24:38.019
from the baby whisperer at this point.

24:38.020 --> 24:39.040
Just sayin'.

24:43.230 --> 24:45.120
I was outbid on the house anyway.

24:46.180 --> 24:47.209
Shit.

24:47.210 --> 24:48.219
Look, Jeannie,

24:48.220 --> 24:50.199
you can move if you want to, obviously.

24:50.200 --> 24:51.189
