26:39.120 --> 26:41.029
I don't even think I
knew it was in Spain.

26:41.030 --> 26:43.219
I just... It sounded so fancy.

26:43.220 --> 26:45.190
We could bring Phoebe.

26:47.200 --> 26:50.089
Uh, I'm not saying "we." I...

26:50.090 --> 26:51.229
- I could her... bring her, or you...
- No, no, no.

26:51.230 --> 26:53.139
- Could bring her separately.
- No, no. No, yeah, no. No.

26:53.140 --> 26:55.139
"We" is... No, we could...
we could bring Phoebe.

26:55.140 --> 26:57.029
