this away from Monica,

27:06.070 --> 27:07.189
she even kills herself.

27:07.190 --> 27:11.219
Now, that is... dark.

27:11.220 --> 27:14.129
- But it's... also...
- But it's good. No, it's good.

27:14.130 --> 27:16.179
Except, she is Roscoe's mother.

27:16.180 --> 27:18.059
